l md:text-7xl font-bold leading-[1.05]\" style=\"opacity:0\">Premium<br/><span class=\"text-[#D4AF37]\">Embroidery</span><br/>Digitizing &amp;<br/>Manufacturing</h1><p class=\"text-zinc-400 text-lg mt-8 max-w-xl leading-relaxed\">Custom patches, embroidery digitizing, sportswear manufacturing, private label apparel production, and premium merchandise solutions for brands worldwide.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-10\"><button class=\"bg-[#D4AF37] text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(212,175,55,0.35)] transition-all\">Get Quote →</button><button class=\"border border-[#D4AF37] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-[#D4AF37] hover:text-black transition-all\">View Portfolio</button></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-16\"><div><h3 class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-[#D4AF37]\">10+</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-500\">Years Experience</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-[#D4AF37]\">5000+</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-500\">Orders Completed</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-[#D4AF37]\">50+</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-500\">Countries Served</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-[#D4AF37]\">99%</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-500\">Satisfaction</p></div></div></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[#D4AF37]/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full\"></div><div class=\"relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-[#D4AF37]/40  shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(212,175,55,0.15)]\"><img alt=\"Luxury Embroidery Manufacturing\" width=\"900\" height=\"1000\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-auto object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero%2Fhero-1.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero%2Fhero-1.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero%2Fhero-1.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 left-6 bg-black/70 backdrop-blur-xl border border-[#D4AF37]/20 p-6 rounded-2xl\"><h4 class=\"text-[#D4AF37] text-xl font-semibold\">Custom Patches</h4><p class=\"text-zinc-400 text-sm mt-2\">Embroidered • PVC • Leather • Woven</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 border-y border-zinc-900\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center\"><div><h3 class=\"text-5xl font-bold text-[#D4AF37]\">15+</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 mt-3\">Years Experience</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-5xl font-bold text-[#D4AF37]\">20K+</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 mt-3\">Orders Completed</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-5xl font-bold text-[#D4AF37]\">50+</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 mt-3\">Countries Served</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-5xl font-bold text-[#D4AF37]\">98%</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 mt-3\">Client Satisfaction</p></div></div></div></section><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px)\"><section id=\"services\" class=\"py-32 bg-black border-t border-zinc-900\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"text-center mb-20\">...</div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"   bg-zinc-950   border   border-zinc-800   rounded-3xl   p-8   hover:border-[#D4AF37]   hover:-translate-y-2   hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.15)]   transition-all   duration-300   \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-pen-tool w-12 h-12 text-[#D4AF37] mb-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15.707 21.293a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-1.586-1.586a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.414l5.586-5.586a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 0l1.586 1.586a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.414z\"></path><path d=\"m18 13-1.375-6.874a1 1 0 0 0-.746-.776L3.235 2.028a1 1 0 0 0-1.207 1.207L5.35 15.879a1 1 0 0 0 .776.746L13 18\"></path><path d=\"m2.3 2.3 7.286 7.286\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Embroidery Digitizing</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed\">Professional embroidery digitizing with clean stitch paths, optimized density, and machine-ready files.</p></div><div class=\"   bg-zinc-950   border   border-zinc-800   rounded-3xl   p-8   hover:border-[#D4AF37]   hover:-translate-y-2   hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.15)]   transition-all   duration-300   \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-12 h-12 text-[#D4AF37] mb-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Custom Patches</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed\">Premium embroidered, woven, PVC and chenille patches manufactured to the highest standards.</p></div><div class=\"   bg-zinc-950   border   border-zinc-800   rounded-3xl   p-8   hover:border-[#D4AF37]   hover:-translate-y-2   hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.15)]   transition-all   duration-300   \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shirt w-12 h-12 text-[#D4AF37] mb-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.38 3.46 16 2a4 4 0 0 1-8 0L3.62 3.46a2 2 0 0 0-1.34 2.23l.58 3.47a1 1 0 0 0 .99.84H6v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h8a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V10h2.15a1 1 0 0 0 .99-.84l.58-3.47a2 2 0 0 0-1.34-2.23z\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Jersey Manufacturing</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed\">Custom sports jerseys and teamwear with full sublimation, embroidery and private labeling.</p></div><div class=\"   bg-zinc-950   border   border-zinc-800   rounded-3xl   p-8   hover:border-[#D4AF37]   hover:-translate-y-2   hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.15)]   transition-all   duration-300   \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-package w-12 h-12 text-[#D4AF37] mb-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11 21.73a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73z\"></path><path d=\"M12 22V12\"></path><polyline points=\"3.29 7 12 12 20.71 7\"></polyline><path d=\"m7.5 4.27 9 5.15\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Private Label Production</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed\">Complete apparel manufacturing solutions for emerging and established brands.</p></div><div class=\"   bg-zinc-950   border   border-zinc-800   rounded-3xl   p-8   hover:border-[#D4AF37]   hover:-translate-y-2   hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.15)]   transition-all   duration-300   \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-layers w-12 h-12 text-[#D4AF37] mb-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12.83 2.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 6.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.83l8.58 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0l8.58-3.9a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.83z\"></path><path d=\"M2 12a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 12\"></path><path d=\"M2 17a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 17\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Vector Conversion</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed\">Convert low-quality artwork into scalable vector files ready for printing and production.</p></div><div class=\"   bg-zinc-950   border   border-zinc-800   rounded-3xl   p-8   hover:border-[#D4AF37]   hover:-translate-y-2   hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.15)]   transition-all   duration-300   \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award w-12 h-12 text-[#D4AF37] mb-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Premium Apparel</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed\">Custom t-shirts, hoodies, hats, gloves and branded merchandise produced globally.</p></div></div></div></section></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px)\"><section id=\"portfolio\" class=\"py-32 bg-black border-t border-zinc-900\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"text-center mb-20\"><p class=\"text-[#D4AF37] uppercase tracking-[4px] text-sm mb-4\">Our Work</p><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white\">Portfolio Showcase</h2><p class=\"text-zinc-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-6\">Explore our premium embroidery digitizing, custom patch manufacturing and apparel production projects delivered to clients worldwide.</p></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"   group   relative   overflow-hidden   rounded-3xl   border   border-zinc-800   bg-zinc-950   hover:border-[#D4AF37]   hover:-translate-y-2   hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.15)]   transition-all   duration-300   \"><div class=\"relative h-[500px]\"><img alt=\"Embroidery Digitizing\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"   object-cover   transition-all   duratio